{"type": "article", "id": 55309, "title": "阿迪达斯承诺到 2024 年只用回收塑料，以及，J.W.Anderson 与匡威联名系列发布 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-07-17T09:06:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2835, "name": "匡威"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 1893, "name": "Crocs"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180717170457YUaIhVygSMPNeKGn.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Eurazeo-invests-60-million-in-Pat-McGrath-Labs,998249.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国美妆品牌&nbsp;Pat McGrath Labs 获法国基金 Eurazeo 6000 万美元投资</a>&nbsp;</strong>|&nbsp;Pat McGrath Labs 将利用这笔资金扩张其在美国的销售渠道，并计划向全球扩张。交易双方并未透露具体细节，但有业内人士称 Eurazeo 购买了该品牌 5% - 8% 的股权，品牌估值达到 10 亿美元。Pat McGrath Labs 成立于 2016，以秀场彩妆著称，去年刚进驻北美丝芙兰，目前在美国的 54 家门店有售，并计划在今年秋天前增至 90 家。包括此次投资，Pat McGrath Labs 获得的外部投资总计达到 8800 万美元（此前投资者为 One Luxury Group）。Eurazeo 目前管理的资产总额达 160 亿欧元，此前投资的时尚及美妆品牌包括 Nest Fragrances、Farfetch、Moncler 以及 Vestiaire Collective。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/73ca70d8-84e1-11e8-96dd-fa565ec55929\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>阿迪达斯承诺到 2024 年只使用回收塑料</strong></a>&nbsp;| 阿迪达斯利用回收塑料瓶材料制成的球鞋首批量产于 2016 年。该公司称今年这些球鞋的销量将达到 500 万双，到 2019 年则将达到 1100 万双。阿迪达斯全球品牌主管&nbsp;Eric Liedtke 表示，阿迪阿斯的 9.2 亿件商品中聚酯纤维占 50% ，因此转变无法很快发生。另外，回收聚酯纤维的价格要比普通聚酯纤维高出 10% - 20%。即便阿迪达斯能够卖出 1100 万双，它们也只会占年产量的 3%。不过有部分从业者相信，两种材质之间的价格差异将随着更多公司改善供应链的可持续性而缩小。<br></p><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Chanel-launches-online-shop-in-the-UK,998203.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chanel 英国官网开通线上购物功能，但仅限于墨镜</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 该功能开通的同时，Chanel 在 伦敦著名奢侈品购物拱廊街 Burlington Arcade 的门店也再度开业。此次出售墨镜的新尝试被认为与 Farfetch 有关。今年早些时候，Chanel 曾宣布将于 Farfetch 合作，推出新的数字化方案、提升实体店消费体验，吸引更多千禧一代顾客。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/victoria-beckham-alexa-chung-bobby-abley-join-london-fashion-week-schedule-1202759274/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Victoria Beckham 以及 AlexaChung 等将加入 9 月伦敦时装周</a></strong> | 伦敦时装周这次的新面孔不少，除了 Victoria Beckham 和 AlexaChung 还有男装设计师 Bobby Abley 和 Kiko Kostadinov。值得一提的是，Victoria Beckham 将于 9 月 16 日发布 2019 春夏系列，庆祝品牌成立 10 周年。Burberry 则将于次日展示创意总监 Riccardo Tisci 上任以来的第一个系列。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.prnasia.com/p/lightnews-1-102-12794.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">奢侈品电商寺库与山东如意集团达成战略合作</a></strong>&nbsp;| 根据通稿中的说法，双方将依托各自在品牌、技术、网络、渠道和上市公司平台方面的资源和能力，围绕品牌运营、大数据与智能制造、智慧新零售等领域开展合作。山东如意集团旗下拥有 Maje、Sandro、Kent&amp;Curwen、Cerruti1881、Gieves&amp;Hawkes 等服装品牌，今年初刚收购瑞士奢侈品牌 Bally。寺库刚于本月初获京东及 LVMH 集团旗下投资公司&nbsp;L Catterton Asia&nbsp;1.75 亿美元投资。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/lifestyle/341334/qingzhushijiebiaoqingfuhaoripingguodailaichaofengfu-emoji-yulan/\" rel=\"nofollow\">为庆祝 7 月 17 日世界表情符号日，苹果在官网公布了 70 多个全新 Emoji 表情</a></strong>。<br></p><p>更新中包括更多发型、更多形态的笑脸，以及更多动物和食物表情，月饼也在其中。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717151430Luqm8EFgQ0y5v9te.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171514408ScktQ62Hao5Lim0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599790\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717151446As7yXk9bgRr3xwLn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599790\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717151502FoOwJUCN1D7SMIr0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599790\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717151510UI8R5LEq3t46wTJB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599790\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/40698/1/these-high-heeled-crocs-are-already-sold-out\" rel=\"nofollow\">广受吐槽的 Crocs 高跟洞洞鞋，售罄了</a></strong>。</p><p>这款名为 Cyprus V Crocs 洞洞鞋有 3.5 寸的高跟，定价 55 美元。虽然在 Twitter 上广受吐槽，但已在品牌官网和亚马逊上迅速售罄。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717170154uI1QGj2xsCTqH0JP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/sneaker/341271/j-w-anderson-x-converse-chuck-70-lianmingxiliezhengshifabu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">J.W.Anderson x CONVERSE Chuck 70 联名系列正式发布</a></strong>。</p><p>新系列灵感来自艺术家 Ron Nagle 的陶瓷和雕塑。4 个鞋款均使用高饱和度的彩色漆皮制作鞋身，高帮版本则制作了渐变效果。鞋带由加宽的毛圈布制成。该系列将于 7 月 19 至 22 日在伦敦的快闪店内发售，随后也将在全球更多地区上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171629232DhKrxYBXy1tEsma.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717162933675iWdBMYXp0f9TR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717162947bXwGB3PDOCQv1Ieq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717162939vEb5sTCx6dtgjMcQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717163011FbmxORhAUIgnlp8o.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717163000Yjeqat3dynPUoILQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717162953gueC2nQYWwj7cDqp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717163029ZMbXnkuo3lt1aDps.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717163041DBflxNgW6218UuOJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717163049Q0tuPIL7MWaRf5iV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717163056x5TJc07kN4qEwVHW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717163106ImNl1WtHjpiraqQC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171631161tweCZk7cPFWfDAj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717163127urjPFwiZsdWNATX4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171631361OyVWhYtXd8FBD7l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502347\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/shows-reviews/gallery/resort-2019-trends-1202736009/#!1/resort-2019-trends\" rel=\"nofollow\">《女装日报》总结了 2019 度假系列的 9 个趋势</a></strong>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717152008n0gHsVmGQ4lUIrMR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><strong>具有层叠感但穿着方便的假多件设计</strong>。从左至右依次为 Fendi、Hellessy、Natasha Zinko 和 Adeam。</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171522496sbTAFGvXRItVJcS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><strong>高饱和度色彩</strong>。从左至右依次为：Rochas, Prabal Gurung, Sonia Rykiel and Victor Glemaud。</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717152636c0DoFXBfkJSA9giV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><strong>不同花朵图案拼接</strong>。从左至右依次为：3.1 Phillip Lim、Louis Vuitton、House of Holland 和 Valentino。</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171524539puWSkL3PihsjwoY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><strong>凸显腰线的收腰西装设计</strong>。从左至右依次为：Mugler、Marina Moscone、Sara Battaglia 和 Chalayan。</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717152622RCLyeSdQWv9ahA37.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><strong>新式剪裁的卡其色风衣</strong>。从左至右依次 为：Preen by Thornton Bregazzi、Pringle of Scotland、Oscar de la Renta 和 Claudia Li。</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018071715291119yEm3PFbqZJhaNj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><strong>用色大胆的波普格纹</strong>。从左至右依次为：Cynthia Rowley、House of Holland、Jil Sander 和 Tibi。</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717153232sbJZ3rIPvgcUVXD0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><strong>带有金属光泽的礼服</strong>。从左至右依次为：BY.Bonnie Young、Baja East、Christian Siriano 和 Bande Noir。</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717153424MjX4LDwVOSRpYW5t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><strong>彩色条纹针织衫</strong>。从左至右依次为：Lela Rose、MSGM、Ports 1961 和 Carolina Herrera。</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717153113G9Qn7MqUiaXEutvW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption><strong>90 年代感印花套装</strong>。从左至右依次为：Chanel、Versace、Iceberg 和 MSGM。</figcaption> </figure></div><p> Dior 公布了第一届“Photography Award for Young Talent”全球青年摄影师大奖的 14 位获奖者。</p><p>该奖项由 Dior 与阿尔勒国家高等摄影学院（École Nationale Supérieure de la Photographie）以及瑞士基金会&nbsp;The Luma Foundation 共同举办。评委中包括知名摄影师 Peter Lindbergh。参赛者的摄影作品必须包含 Dior 品牌的三个元素“色彩、女性和美“。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164102EmXlkCRr0LUhj41s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Yoonkyung Jang</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164542HTJavuY7PqnSFBzG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Yoonkyung Jang</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165519dwKNMk8pIBAjfvz7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Yoonkyung Jang</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164514yeAZasOTR8Kg4M1G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Jai Uk Jung</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164733VnvH2QBuJZdaNt6p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Jai Uk Jung</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164307cMDJwy7gotePqzdv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Yuan Wang</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164616uwCJLa7hqAcZEbor.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Yuan Wang</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171653052vGkTHwtlZKcp9o5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Yuan Wang</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165235i1cNbCHw5qsVeluG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Yuan Wang</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164151ownc26LACs7kTHPE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Hélène Bellenger</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165119cBJDvAhMuLzRa6g5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Hélène Bellenger</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171650085PF7V41jvKbzgryh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.468788\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Sofiya Pankevich</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165153dFfNqPtuWmoOa7gy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.542416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Sofiya Pankevich</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165402iDm8k7Xzlpd96EZ5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.251111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Léia Vandooren</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165602ea2k4TWZDMUwoOht.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Léia Vandooren</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164436EYFn06Ng72MUCmyt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.285556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Sihyun Kim</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165637sV2ltHfd83crwNTv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.285556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Sihyun Kim</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164655DoT9XscQg5OSxnkE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>&nbsp;Loreal Prystal</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165756xQLjM14dYaCZENXK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Loreal Prystal</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171643592vJfTRKhwsMtEkDq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Mai Sakurai</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164931xv7u4THNwX9sUKGE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.670000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Mai Sakurai</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164238WEsZg7aPM8V30cwk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Julien Tucker</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165047j6kvYIXwMEqGzsNT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Julien Tucker</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165831zZDM9K43UgYn6Wwu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Julien Tucker</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164833fVyZ6p0cR8jNioSP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>&nbsp;Khoula Hamad</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717165445Pu9X4ptqLAZWjsFQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>&nbsp;Khoula Hamad</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180717164904AK7wotfOL809kpGx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Wenqingao Reven Lei</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201807171657051dPCpJwzuqVTv9KN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Wenqingao Reven Lei</figcaption> </figure></div><p>题图为&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/art-photography/article/40514/1/peter-lindbergh-dior-beauty-select-their-favourite-emerging-photographers-arles\" rel=\"nofollow\">Khoula Hamad 摄影作品</a></p>"}